                    <h3 className="font-semibold mb-2">Ready to Analyze</h3>
                    <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-sm">
                      Enter your target keyword and content, then click "Analyze Keyword Density" to see detailed insights
                    </p>
                  </CardContent>
